				<td colspan="2"><span>Was wondering what the other swarmers out there are using for spell set up. Just got 54 today and i use
<br />

<br />
1-Charm
<br />
2-Song of Dawn (for mobs that i have over aggroed)
<br />
3-Invis (still looking for that Goblin Gazughi Ring)
<br />
4-Selo's Accelerating Chorus
<br />
5-Dot 1
<br />
6-Dot 2
<br />
7-Dot 3
<br />
8-Dot 4
<br />

<br />
i keep them in the same order on hotkey window with /pet attack @9 and Singing Steel Boots @10.
<br />

<br />
ive found that this works good for me but want to see how others do it also.
<br />

<br />
Caven Coolness
<br />
54 Bard Drinal</span></td>
