				<td colspan="2"><span>1 - Selo's Accelerating Chorus
<br />
2 - hp song/snare slow/dot-slow (depending what I need)
<br />
3-&gt;6 - Dot's
<br />
7 - Occlusion of Sound
<br />
8 - Charm
<br />

<br />
I have SS Boots and Goblin Gazughi Ring.
<br />

<br />
With a lute and brass nearby for when I want to 5 dot or need to pump the hp fast.
<br />

<br />
I am level 61, before 61 one of my dots was a magic debuffing. I like to hit a -MR and then use my flute when charming... seems to do better for me, or at least makes me feel better<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" /></span></td>
